Package: joinless
Title: Exploratory Analysis of Relationships Between Variables
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Braylin Alexander", "Jiménez Reynoso", 
           email = "braylinjr1511@gmail.com", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Braylin Alexander Jiménez Reynoso <braylinjr1511@gmail.com>
Description: Provides tools to explore and summarize relationship patterns between
    variables across one or multiple datasets. The package relies on efficient
    sampling strategies to estimate pairwise associations and supports quick
    exploratory data analysis for large or heterogeneous data sources.
